Package: petroreadr
Type: Package
Title: Read File Formats Used In The Oil Industry
Version: 0.3.0
Author: Francesco Giorgetti
Maintainer: Francesco Giorgetti <frenk.giorgetti@gmail.com>
Description: This package include functions to read common file formats used in 
    the oil&gas industry and converts them into data frames: .las for well logs, 
    ascii grid properties and .gslib grid properties. 
    More formats will be added with time.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
URL: http://www.github.com/frenkg/petroreadr
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Imports: dplyr,
    stringr,
    magrittr,
    R6
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown, 
    roxygen2,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
